name: DailyFashionAdvice
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Daily Fashion Advice is a flash briefing offering tips, tricks, and trend / weather forecasting to help you stay trendy. We cover everything from tips on staying warm in cold weather, to ethical brands, to old trends that are coming back. 

Created by a team of young fashion-forward SAIT (Southern Alberta Institute of Technology) students who are looking to keep you in the loop on the latest. Though some of the information we provide will be directed to Canada specific weather, we still have a global outlook on fashion and what is trending; and will relay the information onto you the best we can!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
